      "text": "- Make everything private\n- Expose single config variable for global use (like\nDjango settings)\n- Config loading fails loudly on startup.\n- Ensure file/directory existence once\n- Maybe config rendering can live inside the Config\nclass itself, so the config can be rendered anywhere",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Make everything private\n- Expose single config variable for global use (like Django settings)\n- Config loading fails loudly on startup.\n- Ensure file/directory existence once\n- Maybe config rendering can live inside the Config class itself, so the config can be rendered anywhere",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
