      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- uses render_config() to get the config as\ntext\n- also calls merge_config and load_toml on the\nconfig file\n- ensures the file path exists (despite already\nusing it beforehand to render config)\n- then ensures the path's parent exists\n- writes config text to file\n- return a boolean",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "xp93lMVC2NC9OZeaGLccG",
      "originalText": "- uses render_config() to get the config as text\n- also calls merge_config and load_toml on the config file\n- ensures the file path exists (despite already using it beforehand to render config)\n- then ensures the path's parent exists\n- writes config text to file\n- return a boolean",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
