      "text": "- acquires session lock\n- fetches session messages\n- uploads attachments\n- packs user question into MessageItem and\nappends it message history\n- sets up tools and system prompts, calls LLM\n- appends tool call output and LLM responses\ninto message history\n- yields all response events to caller",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "tEG70JhP0wVagH6yMagBy",
      "originalText": "- acquires session lock\n- fetches session messages\n- uploads attachments\n- packs user question into MessageItem and appends it message history\n- sets up tools and system prompts, calls LLM\n- appends tool call output and LLM responses into message history\n- yields all response events to caller",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
