      "versionNonce": 601607550,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774873918941,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "takes (chat_key, session_id) and returns/initializes a\nsession\n\n- if a workspace path is provided, the session is anchored\nat that path (even if a previous saved path exists)\n- if a session_id isn't provided, falls back to using the last\nused session id for the chat key, if it exists. Otherwise,\nmints a new UUID (i.e., fresh chat).\n- ensures chat and session folders exist on disk\n- updates messages.json to point to the resolved\nworkspace path\n- sets last used session ID to this session\n- returns the chat_key, session_id pair",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "h9GrNH3n-04Pe-y7zOtjk",
      "originalText": "takes (chat_key, session_id) and returns/initializes a session\n\n- if a workspace path is provided, the session is anchored at that path (even if a previous saved path exists)\n- if a session_id isn't provided, falls back to using the last used session id for the chat key, if it exists. Otherwise, mints a new UUID (i.e., fresh chat).\n- ensures chat and session folders exist on disk\n- updates messages.json to point to the resolved workspace path\n- sets last used session ID to this session\n- returns the chat_key, session_id pair",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
